00:20:29,810 --> 00:20:31,310
Gin-san!! Gin-san...

521
00:20:31,510 --> 00:20:32,360
Where are you?

522
00:20:32,360 --> 00:20:33,310
Are you all right?

523
00:20:33,310 --> 00:20:34,650
Gin-san!!

524
00:20:37,550 --> 00:20:39,040
Thank goodness!

525
00:20:39,040 --> 00:20:42,150
I can't see anything without my glasses, but you're okay, right?

526
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:44,310
I'm sorry...

527
00:20:44,310 --> 00:20:46,170
It's all my fault...

528
00:20:46,170 --> 00:20:52,130
I...was warned that love would interfere with my work.

529
00:20:52,130 --> 00:20:55,010
But I still couldn't get you out of my mind, Gin-san.

530
00:20:55,990 --> 00:20:58,240
But this is what I think...

531
00:20:58,240 --> 00:21:02,340
An assassin who has someone she wants to protect

532
00:21:02,340 --> 00:21:05,380
is more motivated than one who has no one.

533
00:21:05,870 --> 00:21:08,780
That's why, I won't change my ways...

534
00:21:08,780 --> 00:21:10,260
And I'll always...

535
00:21:10,260 --> 00:21:12,250
...keep thinking of you, Gin-san...

536
00:21:14,430 --> 00:21:15,330
Huh?

537
00:21:18,120 --> 00:21:20,360
Killer mode, on!

538
00:22:56,780 --> 00:22:59,040
The next episode, summer ghost stories...

539
00:22:59,040 --> 00:23:01,350
"Like a Haunted House, Life is Filled with Horrors."

540
00:23:01,090 --> 00:23:07,030
[This year's ghosts will be done by Odd Jobs. It will be thrilling in many ways.]

541
00:23:07,030 --> 00:23:11,030
